    <!-- SteamGridDB -->
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGuideStep1Title">1. Open the SteamGridDB API page</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridApiKeyDesc">커버 아트 매칭 정확도를 향상시키는 데 사용됩니다. 선택 사항이지만 권장됩니다.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGuideStep2Title">2. API 키 생성</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGuideStep1Desc">https://www.steamgriddb.com/profile/preferences/api 에 접속하여 로그인하세요.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGuideStep4Desc">키를 저장한 후 새 스캔을 실행하면 커버가 더 정확하게 갱신됩니다.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGetApiKey">API 키 가져오기</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGuideStep2Desc">해당 페이지에서 새 API 키를 생성하고 복사하세요.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGuideOpenPage">페이지 열기</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGuideStep4Title">4. 게임을 다시 스캔하세요</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGuideHeader">Get your SteamGridDB API Key</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGuideTitle">SteamGridDB API Key</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGuideHeaderDesc">게임 커버 감지를 개선하기 위한 빠른 안내서.</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridApiKey">SteamGridDB API Key</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridApiKeyPlaceholder">Paste your SteamGridDB API key here</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGuideStep3Title">3. 설정에 붙여넣기</x:String>
    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGuideStep3Desc">Return to the app and paste the key into the SteamGridDB API Key field.</x:String>

    <x:String x:Key="TxtSteamGridGuideStep1Prefix">다음 페이지로 이동하여 </x:String>
